<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Suihlung hel ni'n khawdak in,
 Khaw tin ngo bang lang tangah galin dawn leng;
 Muol zatam hala len-guol ngaihte samin,
 Gal dawt hi tiu Aw, kumsawt gam ngaia leng I hiu.

[V2]
 Gam nuoma nga bang lengte'n,
 Zuo sau lun ah deih cheng pak bang;
 Lawpin siengah a lawi ui,
 Angel vam lungdeihte tawh ngabang a leng khawm ui.

[V3]
 2. Ka matieng gam ninnuom ah,
 Piellei kala sam bang zalsa a leng ui;
 Lautha tung thakte leh Saron pak a lun,
 Nunnawp pak bang chulsa puon bangin a thak kit tai.

[V4]
 3. I nawp lai niteu a tuoi,
 Lungdeihte I khen vangkhuo giel bang a dai,
 Vangkhuo a lengte singkhuol a chang zo tau ,
 Ka ngai nun lui puon bang chulsa leh kumsawt gam nuom,

[V5]
 4. Suihlung hel leh tang ngomei ,
 A bei thei puoi suihlung ah dai bang a cham;
 Albang dahna sawl ang ka bang ei nemin,
 Mu bang ka ngai Lal nunnem, Saron pak hung lunin.</lyrics>
<title>Angel Vamte Tawh !</title>
<hymn_number>146</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
</song>